metadata.name: Your Mind is a Beautiful Thing
metadata.description:
Your Mind is a Beautiful Thing.
It never stops working.
It always thinks on how to help the family.
It always finds a way to help friends.
It always makes plans for a better future.
It always tries to become better.

You are beautiful, not because of your face or your body, but because you have a beautiful mind.

Mixed media on paper (watercolor & colored pencil), edited in Photoshop.
